        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Sep 1<hi rend="superscript">st</hi></placeName>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I believe my friend M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Peacock of Trin<hi rend="superscript">y</hi> College Camb<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> has succeeded in getting a “Savant” for you— A M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Darwin grandson of the well known philosopher and poet—full of zeal and enterprize and having contemplated a voyage on his own account to S. America</p>
<p>Let me know how you like the idea that I may go or recede in time | F B</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        
